airtrafficcontrol.app.utils

Class AirCorridorInTime

  • java.lang.Object
    • airtrafficcontrol.app.utils.AirCorridorInTime

  • public class AirCorridorInTime
extends java.lang.Object
    Class whose instances represent an air corridor where it is expected that a certain airship flies during a certain period of time. These class's instances are supposed to always be properties of instances of Airship's subclasses.
    Author:
    Eva Gomes, Hugo Leal, Lucas Andrade
